name: Original Suet Fat Balls 12.55kg
amazon_description: Original Suet Fat Balls 12.55kg (equivalent to approx.150)
google_category: Animals & Pet Supplies > Pet Supplies > Bird Supplies > Bird Food
description:
Buy two boxes for even better value!

Composition

Cereals, oil, fat, flour, black sunflower seeds, kibbled corn maize, minerals and mix seeds.

Product Details

The 12.55kg of Original Suet Fat balls, are equivalent to approximately 150 individual fat balls.

Original Flavour Fat Balls are an all-natural blend of beef fat, wheat, sunflower seeds and calcium sourced in the UK, where possible, to provide a high energy and nutritious food source for a wide variety of wild birds. All the ingredients used for the Fatballs are sourced from reputable, local, national UK and international suppliers and are subject to strict quality controls to ensure suitability and quality. The fat in these fat balls is graded as the highest food grade and is packed with energy to help wild birds during demanding times.

The wheat is from local growers and is particularly attractive to the declining Houseparrow as well as many other species. A natural source of calcium is added to standard fat balls to provide wild birds with a means to maintain healthy bones and eggs. Standard Fat Balls are most commonly fed using specially made Fat Ball Feeders. Another method is to break up the fat balls and feed directly from the ground, on bird tables, or mixed with other foods such as Peanuts or Seed Mixes.

These Fat Balls are suitable for all year round feeding and will help a wide variety of wild birds survive through harsh Winters, and busy Spring/Summer breeding seasons in particular. 

Please note; due to carriage and the fragile nature of the product it can be common for up to 10% of fat balls to be broken at the bottom of the box, but don't worry as the birds still eat them all the same.
short_description: An all-natural blend of beef fat, wheat, sunflower seeds and calcium to provide a high energy and nutritious food source for a wide variety of wild birds.

name: Apple iPad Air 2 Grey 16GB
google_category: Electronics > Computers > Tablet Computers
description:
New Apple iPad Air 2 16GB in Space Grey.

The new iPad Air 2 is here, and it's slimmer and more powerful than ever.

Thinnest iPad ever

At just 6.1 mm thick, the Air 2 is Apple's thinnest ever iPad. It's impressively light too, so it's easy to hold in one hand, discretely slip into and bag and take anywhere.

It looks and feels great thanks to its aluminium unibody case, while the wraparound design improves rigidity and keeps the important internals safe when on the go.

All-new display

Unlike previous iPad displays, the Air 2's Retina screen is a single component. This eliminates gaps for a brighter picture with improved clarity and colours. It brings the screen closer to your fingertips for a better touch response when playing games and browsing, so you feel more connected to your content than ever before.

While incredible iPad Air picture quality remains, the iPad Air 2 includes an anti-glare coating that makes it comfortable to use inside, outside and under bright artificial light.

More powerful

Compared to the previous generation, the iPad Air 2 boasts 40% faster performance thanks to the new A8X processor. From turning on and checking your mail to running demanding apps and games, your whole tablet experience is quicker and more responsive.

It features vastly improved graphics too, so photo-editing and modelling apps run at their best along with beautiful everyday surfing and browsing.

Better battery life

Surprisingly, turning up the performance throughout the iPad Air hasn't affected the energy consumption. You still get an all-day 10 battery life that allows you to access the information that matters to you wherever, and whenever, you feel like it.

Fingerprint scanner

Keeping your private information private is quick and easy thanks to the new Touch ID fingerprint scanner - simply swipe your finger over the sensor embedded in the Home button to unlock your account.

iOS 8

The iPad Air 2 comes preinstalled with iOS 8. Featuring a colourful new design, iCloud integration and tons of new features including the ability to send and receive text messages directly from the tablet when paired with an iPhone, it takes the iOS formula you know and makes it better.

There are now well over a million apps available from the App Store, so whatever you're into, the iPad Air 2 has something you'll love.

Enjoy the most powerful and compact iPad ever with the iPad Air 2.
short_description: Apple iPad Air 2 Grey 16GB

name: Apple 16GB iPad Mini Silver – Wi-Fi with Retina Display
google_category: Electronics > Computers > Tablet Computers
description:
New Apple 16GB iPad Mini - Wi-Fi with Retina Display in Silver.

The 16GB iPad mini 2 with Retina Display from Apple has a smaller form factor than its big brother, the iPad Air. The iPad mini 2 is just 7.5mm thin and weighs less than 1 pound. Its smaller form factor makes it easier to hold in one hand. The iPad mini 2 comes in a space gray finish.

The 7.9" Retina Display makes its debut on the iPad mini 2, maintaining its enormous 2048 x 1536 native resolution. At 326 pixels per inch, the Retina Display can show up to 3.1 million pixels at a time. The Retina Display is also a capacitive touchscreen so you'll be able to utilize all the multi-touch gestures of iOS 7.

While the iPad mini 2 may have a smaller form factor than the iPad Air, it still has the same dual-core A7 chip. Apple introduces the 64-bit architecture with the A7 chip, allowing for more robust and powerful apps. In fact, the A7 chip runs four times faster than the previous generation iPad mini. Also, the A7 chip supports OpenGL ES version 3.0 so the iPad mini 2 can enable detailed graphics and visual effects once only possible on desktop computers and game consoles.

The A7 chip is accompanied by the M7 coprocessor, which measures the motion of the iPad mini 2. By pulling data from the accelerometer, gyroscope and compass, it lightens the load of the A7 chip. This frees up the A7 chip to focus on processing multiple tasks and maintaining fast performance. The iPad mini 2 may have the Retina Display, but it still manages to maintain its 10-hour battery life. That's because the A7 chip isn't just more powerful, it's also more efficient.

The iPad mini 2 comes with iOS 7. Apple refined the typography, redrew every icon around a new grid system, and added a precise color palette for a minimalist design. iOS 7 also introduces features, such as the Control Center. The Control Center can be accessed by swiping up from the bottom of the screen and grants you access to the most common setting options, such as Airplane mode, Wi-Fi, Airplay and even a flashlight. iOS 7 also introduces iTunes Radio (only available in the United States), a music streaming service from Apple. You can build your own stations and listen to your favorite songs. You can also view the history of everything you've heard and added to your Wish List and then download them off iTunes.

With iCloud, you can sync your iPad mini 2 to your other iOS devices and Mac computers. Push photos, download apps and continue from where you left off in iBooks with iCloud. iCloud also offers cloud storage so you can back up your contacts, photos and important documents to Apple's cloud servers. You can restore your iPad mini 2 to a previous state using iCloud.
short_description: Apple 16GB iPad Mini Silver – Wi-Fi with Retina Display
product_name: Apple 16GB iPad Mini Silver – Wi-Fi with Retina Display

name: Science Project Kits
google_category: Toys & Games > Toys > Educational Toys > Science Sets
description:
Make your child's playtime fun and educational with this unique collection of four different science projects. The collection includes the Banana Powered Clock Experiment Kit, the Salt Water Powered Car Experiment Kit and the Wind Powered Car Experiment Kit.

Features:

The Banana Powered Clock Experiment Kit: is a great fun and functional item - a banana powered clock! No batteries required (although you will need bananas!) Kit contains digital clock, wiring, copper and zinc strips and tape.

The Salt Water Powered Car Experiment Kit: is the smallest, least expensive, not to mention first fuel cell car to be powered by salt water, the Salt Water Powered Car Experiment Kit gives children a chance to learn about new forms of clean energy, while building and powering their very own toy: Just add salt water and go! After activating the fuel cell module with a salt water mixture, the magnesium metal sheet (3 sheets included) can operate the car for about 5-7 hours continuously. If you want to park the vehicle, simply take out the fuel cell module and rinse with tap water and dry. All the materials used in this kit are environmentally safe and clean, non-toxic substances. It will not produce heat, so it is completely safe for child's play.

The Wind Powered Car Experiment Kit: allows you to create your very own wind powered car and understand the importance of the environmentally friendly power source moving the car. The contents of this kit are gear 1, gear 2, long hexagonal axis, small hexagonal axis, plastic board A, plastic board B, propeller, tail and stickers.

Package content either:

  • 1 x Banana Powered Clock Experiment Kit - Power a clock without the use of batteries
  • Salt Water Powered Car Experiment Kit -Power your own toy car with salt water
  • Car will run for 5-7 hours continuously
  • Wind Powered Car Experiment Kit
  • Power your own toy car using wind power
  • Suitable for ages 10+
short_description: Science Project Kits

name: Original Suet Fat Balls 26.10kg
amazon_description: Original Suet Fat Balls 26.10kg (equivalent to approx.300)
google_category: Animals & Pet Supplies > Pet Supplies > Bird Supplies > Bird Food
description:
Buy two boxes for even better value!

Composition

Cereals, oil, fat, flour, black sunflower seeds, kibbled corn maize, minerals and mix seeds.

Product Details

The 26.1kg of Original Suet Fat balls, are equivalent to approximately 300 individual fat balls.

Original Flavour Fat Balls are an all-natural blend of beef fat, wheat, sunflower seeds and calcium sourced in the UK, where possible, to provide a high energy and nutritious food source for a wide variety of wild birds. All the ingredients used for the Fatballs are sourced from reputable, local, national UK and international suppliers and are subject to strict quality controls to ensure suitability and quality. The fat in these fat balls is graded as the highest food grade and is packed with energy to help wild birds during demanding times.

The wheat is from local growers and is particularly attractive to the declining Houseparrow as well as many other species. A natural source of calcium is added to standard fat balls to provide wild birds with a means to maintain healthy bones and eggs. Standard Fat Balls are most commonly fed using specially made Fat Ball Feeders. Another method is to break up the fat balls and feed directly from the ground, on bird tables, or mixed with other foods such as Peanuts or Seed Mixes.

These Fat Balls are suitable for all year round feeding and will help a wide variety of wild birds survive through harsh Winters, and busy Spring/Summer breeding seasons in particular. 

Please note; due to carriage and the fragile nature of the product it can be common for up to 10% of fat balls to be broken at the bottom of the box, but don't worry as the birds still eat them all the same.
short_description: An all-natural blend of beef fat, wheat, sunflower seeds and calcium to provide a high energy and nutritious food source for a wide variety of wild birds.

amazon_description: Case of 6 Bottles Pavone Extra Dry Gold Label Prosecco - Lowest UK Price - 1 Case consisting of 6 Bottles
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Sparkling Wine
description:
A beautiful, and just as popular, and often less expensive comparison to Champagne.

Prosecco is a deliciously dry sparkling wine with crisp acidity, low sugar, with plenty of fruit and character.

Associated with high value at low cost, Prosecco is the perfect option in situations where you want or need a sparkling wine.

Prosecco is both a grape variety, and a wine region, in northern Italy.

Over recent years, it has become known as the definitive brand name for Italian sparkling wine, arguably the most successful wine launch in recent years.

Where Cava reigned supreme for the last 15 years, as the affordable alternative to Champagne, Prosecco has now taken over that mantle.
short_description:

Ideal for Birthday celebrations,Christmas,Weddings or just on a Summers Evening
product_name: Case of 6 Bottles Pavone Extra Dry Gold Label Prosecco - Less than half price - £5.99 per bottle

name: Barolo Antica Cantina le Lodole Red Wine
amazon_description: Barolo Antica Cantina le Lodole Red Wine - DOC Denominazione di Origine Controllata
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine
description:
Barolo is a red wine. It has been named the “the wine of kings” and the “king of wines” by wine experts across the globe. The DOC – Denominazione di Origine Controllata, which is the Italian quality assurance label for wines states that Barolo wine must be produced from 100% Nebbiolo grape and has to age for a minimum of 3 years before being available to buy. The three years includes two years of ageing in a barrel and one year resting in the bottle.

Barolo Antica Cantina le Lodole is a delicious red wine from the Piedmont region of Northern Italy. It is made strictly from Nebbiolo grapes.

Aromatic with rich tannins and characteristics of old oak, these wines are considered by most to be some Italy's finest.
short_description: Barolo Antica Cantina le Lodole is an excellent red wine of rich tannins and characteristics of old oak, considered by most to be some of Italy's finest.
product_name: Barolo Antica Cantina le Lodole Red Wine

name: Barolo La Cacciatora Red Wine
amazon_description: Barolo La Cacciatora Red Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine
description:
One of the most respected and sought-after Italian wines.

Barolo La Cacciatora has a deep ruby red colour with aromas of ripe red fruits, violets with a hint of oak. The taste is full with a strong character featuring hints of tannin, turning velvety with age.

The perfect wine for roasted and braised red meats.
short_description: Barolo La Cacciatora is a strong charactered wine featuring hints of tannin,  perfect for roasted and braised red meats.

name: Fosco Diano D'Alba Red Wine
amazon_description: Fosco Diano D'Alba Red Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine
description:
Fosco Diano D'Alba 2011 is an intense ruby red colour with violet hues. It has a clear and persistent bouquet with scents of gillyflower and matured blackberry. To the taste, Fosco Diano D'Alba is an intense, round, hot and sweet with almond after-taste.

It goes well with both white and red meats, pasta and also with cheese.
short_description: Fosco Diano D'Alba is an intense, round, hot and sweet  with almond after-taste. It goes well with both white and red meats, pasta and also with cheese.

google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > White Wine

A bouquet of with peach and cashew nuts with hints of vanilla from the delicate use of French oak. The palate is medium bodied, rich and complex showing attractive peach and melon fruit, finishing dry with clean fresh acidity.

amazon_description: Wallaby Creek Cabernet Sauvignon Red Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine

A soft, easy-drinking red wine displaying a fine balance of Shiraz and Cabernet Sauvignon grapes. A good quality Australian red full of easy drinking fruitful characters.

The Cabernet exhibits a bouquet of ripe blackberry and cassis characteristics balanced by a hint of mint and light vanilla. The taste is medium-bodied finishing smoothly with soft, well rounded tannins and acidity.

Great with beef, lamb, poultry and spicy dishes.

name: Wallaby Creek Fruity White Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > White Wine
description:
The colour of this Wallaby Creek Fruity White Wine is straw green with a golden tinge. The bouquet shows ripe, fresh, grassy and floral characters enhanced by the fresh apricot fragrance of ripe unwooded Chardonnay and the perfume of ripe Semillon. The palate is sweet, fruity, crisp and clean, light to medium bodied with a crisp acid. It finishes with the sweetness and honey characters of rich grapes.

An excellent accompaniment to Asian and Thai cuisine, white meats, fish and fresh seafood dishes. Best served chilled.
short_description: Wallaby Creek Fruity White Wine, an excellent accompaniment to Asian and Thai cuisine with white meats fish and seafood dishes.

name: CorteReale Morgante Nero d'Avola Red Wine
amazon_description: CorteReale Morgante Nero d'Avola Red Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine
description:
After accumulating generations of grape-growing expertise, the Morgante family started bottling their own wine under the guidance of Riccardo Cotarella in the mid-1990s. Situated in the western reaches of Sicily, where Nero d’Avola reaches optimal ripeness levels, Morgante has crafted this beautiful 100% estate-grown Nero d'Avola wine.

This wine is an intense ruby-red in color with aromas of ripe black cherries and blackberries and hints of vanilla, peppery spice, and smoke. On the palate, abundant flavors of ripe fruit and exotic spices are balanced by a pleasing acidity and silky tannins.

Delicious with roasted meats, mushroom sauces, caponata spreads, and eggplant parmigiana.
short_description: The CorteReale Morgante Nero d'Avola  is an intense ruby-red in color with aromas of ripe black cherries and blackberries and hints of vanilla, peppery spice, and smoke.
product_name: CorteReale Morgante Nero d'Avola Red Wine

name: Velvet Lake Red Wiine
amazon_description: Velvet Lake Red Wiine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Red Wine
description:
Velvet Lake has launched a range of “sweet but well balanced” Australian red, white and rosé wines into retailers across the UK.



This red wine features a ripe, red berry fruit with a hint of raspberry, spice and chocolate - full, rich flavour.



Perfect for most occasions from a quiet cosy night in, to your summer barbie or garden party. With its ripe, juicy fruit flavour, this wine is great with most moderate to fully flavoured dishes, including pasta and pizza, barbecued burgers and sausages. But very nice as an apéro with a plate of crisps…
short_description: This red wine features a ripe, red berry fruit with a hint of raspberry, spice and chocolate - full, rich flavour.

name: Velvet Lake Rosé Wine
amazon_description: Velvet Lake Rosé Wine
google_category: Food, Beverages & Tobacco > Beverages > Wine > Rosé Wine
description:
Velvet Lake has launched a range of “sweet but well balanced” Australian red, white and rosé wines into retailers across the UK.

Perfect for most occasions but great for a birthday party or girl’s night in. With its summery fruit flavour, this wine is good with most moderate to lightly flavoured dishes, including pasta, couscous and creamy risottos. But very nice as an apéro with a big bowl of buttery popcorn to pass around…

Rosé or pink wines are the result of the fermentation of grape juice, grape extract, or black grapes in order to give the wine a touch of pink colour, as well as a slightly tannic flavour. Pink wines can also be obtained by mixing a white wine with a red wine.

Colour : Pale bronze with watermelon hues
Aroma : Nectarine, dandelion and strawberry notes
Palate : Stone fruit with light berry flavours and a smooth balanced finish
short_description: Velvet Lake Rosé is perfect for most occasions but great for parties. With its summery fruit flavour, the wine is ideal for pasta, couscous or risotto dishes.

But very nice as an apéro with a big bowl of buttery popcorn to pass around…

Rosé or pink wines are the result of the fermentation of grape juice, grape extract, or black grapes in order to give the wine a touch of pink colour, as well as a slightly tannic flavour. Pink wines can also be obtained by mixing a white wine with a red wine.

Colour : Pale bronze with watermelon hues
Aroma : Nectarine, dandelion and strawberry notes
Palate : Stone fruit with light berry flavours and a smooth balanced finish
short_description: Velvet Lake Rosé is perfect for most occasions but great for parties. With its summery fruit flavour, the wine is ideal for pasta, couscous or risotto dishes.

name: Black PS4 Batman: Arkham Knight Bundle + Bonus Mission Pack [Pre-order]
amazon_description: Black Playstation 4, Batman: Arkham Knight Bundle + Bonus Scarecrow Nightmare Mission Pack.
google_category: Electronics > Video Game Consoles
description:
Please note: this a pre-order for release June 23rd 2015. Order before Friday 19th for delivery on launch day.

The PS4--ten times more powerful than the PS3--is the world’s most powerful games console. Within its sleek and compact shell lies a 500GB hard drive, full HD (1080p) capability, superior speed and graphics, and an internal power supply to save you space. The PS4 also delivers amazing online experiences, and the best choice of blockbuster and indie games in the market. With 5-star reviews across the board, from the likes of Stuff magazine, a People’s Choice Award from IGN readers, and T3’s Gadget of the Year Award, the PS4 truly is the best place to play.

Batman: Arkham Knight

Batman: Arkham Knight brings the award-winning Arkham trilogy from Rocksteady Studios to its epic conclusion, developed exclusively for next-gen platforms.

Live the complete Batman experience as the Dark Knight enters the concluding chapter of Rocksteady's Arkham trilogy.

Players will become the world's greatest detective like never before with the introduction of the Batmobile and enhancements to signature features such as FreeFlow Combat, stealth, forensics, and navigation.

In this explosive finale, Batman faces the ultimate threat against the city that he is sworn to protect, as Scarecrow returns to unite the super criminals of Gotham and destroy the Batman forever.

This console also includes the Scarecrow Nightmare Mission Pack. In the Scarecrow Nightmare, you will be able to play three extra missions. As a solar eclipse plunges Gotham into darkness, you'll need all the Batmobile's arsenal to face off against a monstrous 100-foot Scarecrow and his army.
short_description: Black PS4 Batman: Arkham Knight Bundle + Bonus Scarecrow Nightmare Mission Pack. Live the final, epic chapter of Rocksteady Studio's Arkham Trilogy.
